  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0db6\u0ddd\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd6\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A statement from the police headquarters about the Borella church bomb",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Media Division says that all the three persons involved in planting the bomb in Borella All Saints Church have been arrested and no strongman of the previous government is involved.",
        "The division also mentions that media reports were being published that justice was not served regarding the bomb incident and that strongmen of the previous government were involved.",
        "In connection with this incident, four persons who worked in the church were arrested and remanded after being presented to the court. The police said that the four suspects were later released according to the instructions of the Attorney General.",
        "Then C.C. A resident of Kadavata area, who was identified in the investigations using TV footage, was arrested in Embilipitiya area on January 16th and remanded after being produced in court.",
        "After that, a doctor from Piliyandala area was arrested on January 17th and remanded after being presented to the Aluthkade Magistrate Court. Then, a 55-year-old suspect residing in Ranna area was arrested on January 20th and remanded after being presented to the Aluthkade Magistrate Court. mentions",
        "The police headquarters said that after hearing the case on the 5th of June, it will be called again on the 13th of September."
      ],
